                    <head>233. Minutes of Washington Special Actions Group Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d233fn1">Source: National Archives, <persName corresp="#p_NRM1">Nixon</persName> Presidential Materials, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (H-Files), Box H–114, <gloss target="#t_WSAG1">WSAG</gloss> Minutes, Originals, 1969–1970. Top
                            Secret; Sensitive. The meeting was held in the White House Situation
                            Room.</note>
                    </head>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right">
                            <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" from="1970-04-15T17:22:00-05:00" to="1970-04-15T18:06:00-05:00">April 15, 1970, 5:22–6:06 p.m.</date>
